## Template Updates

This project was scaffolded from [gallop-systems/nuxt-copier-template](https://github.com/gallop-systems/nuxt-copier-template).

The `.github/workflows/check-template-updates.yml` workflow runs daily to check for upstream template changes. When updates are available, it automatically opens a PR with instructions.

To apply template updates:
```bash
# Checkout the PR branch
git checkout chore/template-update-YYYYMMDD
git pull

# Apply updates
copier update --trust

# Review changes, commit, and push
git add -A
git commit -m "chore: apply template updates"
git push
```

The PR includes a link to view what changed in the template since your last update.
